        <div class="ed-hero-text"><div class="ed-label">Writing</div><h2 class="ed-title">Tier Heart Wetness</h2><p class="ed-excerpt">Human and other natures. The practice's first real-time composed piece — ten fragments shaped across a single session. Wonderful Garbage in motion.</p><span class="ed-cta">Read piece</span></div>
