        <article class="ed-card" data-target="puppets"><div class="ed-card-image"><svg viewBox="0 0 600 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect width="600" height="400" fill="#1a0a00"/><line x1="150" y1="0" x2="150" y2="400" stroke="#3a2810" stroke-width="1"/><line x1="300" y1="0" x2="300" y2="400" stroke="#3a2810" stroke-width="1"/><line x1="450" y1="0" x2="450" y2="400" stroke="#3a2810" stroke-width="1"/></svg></div><div class="ed-label">Theater</div><h3 class="ed-card-title">We Are Not Going Anywhere</h3><p class="ed-card-desc">Ten puppets, one stage, no exits. Underground theater beneath Malheur National Forest. The light comes through damage.</p></article>
